Dear Hiring Team,

It is with great pleasure that I submit my candidacy for the *Full Stack Java Developer* role with *Amex*. I bring over three years of software engineering experience across full-stack systems, cloud-native backend services, and AI-enabled developer platforms, along with a Master of Science in Computer Science from Pace University.

